          ul
            li
              img(src='/images/ymh.png')
              div.info
                div.title
                  h4 Minhong YU
                  p Founder of the New Oriental Education & Technology Group／Founder of Aplus Capital
                div.description
                  p Mr.YU Minghong Founded the New Oriental Education & Technology Group in 1993 which has developed into the largest and most influential brand and leader in private education industry;
                  p New Oriental Education & Technology Group was listed on NYSE in 2006, and is the China's first education and training institutions listed in the United States;
                  p Founded Aplus Capital together with Mr. SHENG Xitai
            li
              img(src='/images/sxt.png')
              div.info
                div.title
                  h4 Xitai SHENG
                  p Senior investment banker / founder of Hongtai Fund
                div.description
                  p Mr. SHENG Xitai has led two securities companies to develop into leading position companies, and he is the former chairman of Huatai United Securities
                  p Mr. SHENG Xitai has more than 20 years’ experience in IPO and M&A of hundreds of cases. He cultivated the best M&A team in China's capital market and also cultivated dozens of industry-leading listed companies, sush as Zoomlion, Han's laser and BlueFocus
                  p Founded Aplus Capital together with Mr. YU Minhong
            li
