                  p Hongtai Fund Partner / Hongtai Chi Foundry Founder
                div.description
                  p Mr.QIAO Huijun is a well-known angel investor in the era of artificial intelligence and the Deputy Director of Artificial Intelligence Industry Innovation Alliance. Mr. QIAO has provided long-term services to the world's major telecom operators and is experienced in R&D, supply chain management, etc.
