            div.b
              div.a
                img(src='/images/jj.png').a1
                h3 洪泰智造基金
                p 洪泰智造基金由俞敏洪、盛希泰和乔会君共同发起，组织形式为有限合伙。主要投资方向为人工智能、智能制造、物联网等相关行业的早中期科技项目。目前已经投出三角兽、TuringSense、智能一点、尺度新媒体等极具潜力的明星创业公司。
              div.a
                img(src='/images/zzgc.png').a1
                h3 洪泰智造工场
                p 洪泰智造工场以领先的“投资+深度服务”的运营模式，为创业者提供全新的服务形态，为硬件创业者提供小批量试产服务。包括产品定义、产品研发、生产以及通过吸收和借鉴全球先进的营销经验与思维，构建全新的营销体系等，输出全流程、全要素、全生命周期的深度创业服务。
            div.b
              div.a
                img(src='/images/wlc.png').a1
                h3 洪泰未来城
                p 洪泰未来城以智能制造生产基地为核心；以智能智造基金和产业基金为杠杆；以洪泰智造工场从孵化到成长到成熟全产业链的服务及全球行业资源为支撑； 以未来城内的智慧生活、智慧城市、智能交通为展示，综合打造一个标准化、专业化、智慧化、聚合智能制造上下游产业资源的立体生态圈。
              div.a
                img(src='/images/zhzx.png').a1
                h3 洪泰智慧中心
                p 洪泰智慧中心专注服务于科技创新型领域的成长期团队，重点领域包括人工智能、智能硬件、智慧城市等。通过集成洪泰丰富的资源和先进的理念，致力于打造规模大、效益好、运营佳的科技企业聚集地。
        - else if (lang === 'en')
          h3 Strategic map
          div.content
            div.b
              div.a
                img(src='/images/jj.png').a1
                h3 Aplus Labs Manufacturing Fund
                p Mr. YU Minhoong, SHENG Xitai and QIAO Huijun founded Aplus Intelligence and Manufacturing Fund, and organized the fund with limited partnership pattern. This fund focuses on early stage and mid-term projects on AI, Intelligent Manufacturing, IoT, etc. Aplus Labs provide start-ups with fund and deep services, and provide not only incubation areas, but also professional engineers, agile production lines (labs) and APL system.
              div.a
                img(src='/images/zzgc.png').a1
                h3 Aplus Labs
                p Aplus Labs is the world's leading AI and intelligent manufacturing entrepreneurship services platform.  With the unique operating system of "investment + deep services", Aplus Labs provide a new form of services chain and trial production services for the start-ups. These services include product definition, R&D, production, and building a new marketing system through the absorption and learning from the global advanced marketing experience. Aplus Labs provide a whole process, all-round, and life cycle deep services.
            div.b
              div.a
                img(src='/images/wlc.png').a1
                h3 Aplus Exiderdome
                p Aplus Exiderdome will be allocated with world top fully automatic (the fourth industrial revolution) Intelligent Manufacturing Bases, Intelligence and Manufacturing Fund, Industrial Investment Fund and services and global resources on a whole industry chain which supports the development of start-ups. The core objective will be establishing high-level, professional and intelligent integrated industry ecosystems with the idea of exiderdome and connecting upstream and downstream |industry resources on IM, which is realized by intelligent life, smart city and ITS.
              div.a
                img(src='/images/zhzx.png').a1
                h3 Aplus Smart Centers
                p Aplus Smart Centers mainly provide services on high-tech developing businesses on AI, intelligent hardware, smart city, etc., and will be expanding, highly productive and well-operated high tech clusters.
